The global automotive ambient lighting market is anticipated to experience substantial growth by the year 2030. The market is segmented based on electric vehicle type, application, and geography. Electric vehicle types include Battery Electric Vehicle (BEV), Hybrid Electric Vehicle (HEV), and Plug-In Hybrid Electric Vehicle (PHEV). Ambient lighting applications in vehicles can be found in areas such as footwells, doors, dashboard, center console, and reading lights. Geographically, the market spans across regions including North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, South America, and the Middle East and Africa.

